    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a great opportunity for someone seeking reliable transportation at an affordable price! While it shows some honest signs of use and character from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional car that's perfect for your everyday needs.",
