      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's looking for a brand new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s a smooth ride that\u2019s been well-cared for, making it perfect for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve loved driving this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
