    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring a pure analog connection to the tarmac. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains composed with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in characteristics this platform is famous for. While the body shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including consistent compression and cooling system integrity\u2014are sorted. This is a mechanically robust specimen ready for the technical curves of a backroad or the rigors of a track day.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
