    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly captures the balance of reliability and style. This car has been my dependable daily driver, and it shows in its smooth mechanical performance. The engine starts instantly and idles quietly, with no leaks or warning lights on the dashboard. The transmission is responsive, providing seamless shifts whether you're navigating city traffic or cruising on the highway. On the exterior, the paint holds a beautiful gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing, the body is straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary. The upholstery is in great shape with no tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster consistent with regular use. Every feature works as intended, from the ice-cold air conditioning and heated seats to the premium sound system. It comes with a documented service history, including a recent oil change and a fresh set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles of trouble-free driving.",
      "price": 32800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
